<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>国土报最新头条</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news</link><description></description><lastBuildDate>Sun, 29 Oct 2023 00:32:48 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>以色列人质的时间不多了，他们的家人“厌倦了口号”</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/opinion/editorial/2023-10-29/ty-article/israels-hostages-are-running-out-of-time-and-their-families-are-sick-of-slogans/0000018b-77c3-d1da-a1bb-7ffb0e430000</link><description></description><pubDate>Sun, 29 Oct 2023 00:05:39 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/opinion/editorial/2023-10-29/ty-article/israels-hostages-are-running-out-of-time-and-their-families-are-sick-of-slogans/0000018b-77c3-d1da-a1bb-7ffb0e430000</guid></item><item><title>本格维尔在政治活动中发放枪支后，美国威胁要停止供应枪支</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-28/ty-article/.premium/u-s-threatens-to-stop-supplying-guns-after-ben-gvir-gives-them-out-at-political-events/0000018b-77eb-d1da-a1bb-7ffb96dc0000</link><description>以色列国家安全部长伊塔马尔·本·格维尔的社交媒体帖子显示，他向宗教右翼占主导地位的地区的平民分发步枪</description><pubDate>Sat, 28 Oct 2023 20:56:02 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-28/ty-article/.premium/u-s-threatens-to-stop-supplying-guns-after-ben-gvir-gives-them-out-at-political-events/0000018b-77eb-d1da-a1bb-7ffb96dc0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列的战争迷雾导致加沙混乱，但没有它就无法实现其目标</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-28/ty-article/.premium/israels-fog-of-war-leads-to-chaos-in-gaza-but-its-goals-wont-be-achieved-without-it/0000018b-77ba-d4a8-a3cf-ffbbc6b80000</link><description>以色列国防军部队进入加沙地带北部，国防官员估计哈马斯领导层似乎醉心于权力，并没有真正的兴趣释放人质以换取以色列境内的囚犯和人道主义援助</description><pubDate>Sat, 28 Oct 2023 20:38:06 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-28/ty-article/.premium/israels-fog-of-war-leads-to-chaos-in-gaza-but-its-goals-wont-be-achieved-without-it/0000018b-77ba-d4a8-a3cf-ffbbc6b80000</guid></item><item><title>特朗普在共和党犹太人峰会上表示欢迎，并发誓要取消亲巴勒斯坦抗议者的签证</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/us-news/2023-10-28/ty-article/trump-hailed-at-republican-jewish-summit-vows-to-cancel-pro-palestinian-protesters-visas/0000018b-77cd-d51e-a3cb-77ed26c80000</link><description>这位前总统在共和党犹太联盟会议上发誓要停止第三次世界大战，并在谈到哈马斯 10 月 7 日袭击的受害者时表示：“他们会受到复仇，甚至超出你的想象。”</description><pubDate>Sat, 28 Oct 2023 20:10:01 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/us-news/2023-10-28/ty-article/trump-hailed-at-republican-jewish-summit-vows-to-cancel-pro-palestinian-protesters-visas/0000018b-77cd-d51e-a3cb-77ed26c80000</guid></item><item><title>随着夏令时结束，以色列将夜间时钟调回周日</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-28/ty-article/israel-to-turn-back-clocks-overnight-into-sunday-as-daylight-saving-time-ends/0000018b-77c5-d2fc-adcf-f7df41630001</link><description>周日凌晨 2:00，时钟将恢复至凌晨 1:00</description><pubDate>Sat, 28 Oct 2023 19:56:55 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-28/ty-article/israel-to-turn-back-clocks-overnight-into-sunday-as-daylight-saving-time-ends/0000018b-77c5-d2fc-adcf-f7df41630001</guid></item><item><title>人质家属告诉内塔尼亚胡释放巴勒斯坦囚犯是唯一选择</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-28/ty-article/.premium/hostages-families-tell-netanyahu-releasing-palestinian-prisoners-is-only-option/0000018b-77b0-d1da-a1bb-7fb80e600000</link><description>加沙哈马斯扣押人质的亲人代表告诉以色列总理，他们支持一项全面协议，并相信这将得到全国的大力支持</description><pubDate>Sat, 28 Oct 2023 19:43:13 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-28/ty-article/.premium/hostages-families-tell-netanyahu-releasing-palestinian-prisoners-is-only-option/0000018b-77b0-d1da-a1bb-7fb80e600000</guid></item><item><title>迈克·彭斯在共和党犹太人会议上退出总统竞选</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/us-news/2023-10-28/ty-article/.premium/mike-pence-withdraws-from-presidential-race-at-republican-jewish-conference/0000018b-7788-d4a8-a3cf-ffa98f7e0000</link><description>这位前副总统的亲以色列政策观点可以追溯到很多年前，他在宣布退出时在讲话中谈到了美国“最珍惜的盟友以色列”</description><pubDate>Sat, 28 Oct 2023 18:56:57 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/us-news/2023-10-28/ty-article/.premium/mike-pence-withdraws-from-presidential-race-at-republican-jewish-conference/0000018b-7788-d4a8-a3cf-ffa98f7e0000</guid></item><item><title>共和党候选人拉马斯瓦米在拉斯维加斯犹太会议上捍卫对以色列的看法</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/us-news/2023-10-28/ty-article/.premium/republican-candidate-ramaswamy-defends-views-on-israel-to-jewish-conference/0000018b-7753-d2fc-adcf-f75f0e4b0000</link><description>维韦克·拉马斯瓦米呼吁美国停止对以色列的军事援助，并质疑美国对加沙战争的支持，他告诉共和党犹太联盟，他的观点绝不是反以色列的</description><pubDate>Sat, 28 Oct 2023 18:05:22 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/us-news/2023-10-28/ty-article/.premium/republican-candidate-ramaswamy-defends-views-on-israel-to-jewish-conference/0000018b-7753-d2fc-adcf-f75f0e4b0000</guid></item><item><title>马斯克表示星链将通过援助组织支持加沙通信连接</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/us-news/2023-10-28/ty-article/musk-says-starlink-will-support-gaza-communications-links-through-aid-groups/0000018b-76e3-d51e-a3cb-77ef7c900000</link><description>这位亿万富翁表示，SpaceX 将与“国际公认的援助组织”合作，为加沙提供连接，那里的电话和互联网中断导致人们与世隔绝。</description><pubDate>Sat, 28 Oct 2023 16:46:05 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/us-news/2023-10-28/ty-article/musk-says-starlink-will-support-gaza-communications-links-through-aid-groups/0000018b-76e3-d51e-a3cb-77ef7c900000</guid></item><item><title>土耳其百年诞辰黯然失色，埃尔多安在亲巴勒斯坦集会上表示：以色列是占领者</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/middle-east-news/2023-10-28/ty-article/eclipsing-turkeys-centenary-erdogan-tells-pro-palestinian-rally-israel-is-occupier/0000018b-76ff-d2fc-adcf-f7ffb68a0000</link><description>埃尔多安邀请所有土耳其人参加集会，他说“只有我们的旗帜和巴勒斯坦旗帜会飘扬”，试图掩盖定于第二天举行的世俗共和国百年庆典</description><pubDate>Sat, 28 Oct 2023 16:43:26 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/middle-east-news/2023-10-28/ty-article/eclipsing-turkeys-centenary-erdogan-tells-pro-palestinian-rally-israel-is-occupier/0000018b-76ff-d2fc-adcf-f7ffb68a0000</guid></item><item><title>加沙战争暴力升级，以色列定居者杀死在约旦河西岸收割橄榄的巴勒斯坦人</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-28/ty-article/.premium/settler-kills-palestinian-harvesting-olives-in-west-bank-as-violence-rises-amid-gaza-war/0000018b-769e-d4a8-a3cf-febfb9800000</link><description>自 10 月 7 日哈马斯袭击以来，约旦河西岸定居者与巴勒斯坦人之间的对抗有所增加，安全部门消息人士称此类事件损害了以色列的合法性</description><pubDate>Sat, 28 Oct 2023 14:42:40 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-28/ty-article/.premium/settler-kills-palestinian-harvesting-olives-in-west-bank-as-violence-rises-amid-gaza-war/0000018b-769e-d4a8-a3cf-febfb9800000</guid></item><item><title>以色列左派的观念也崩溃了</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/opinion/2023-10-28/ty-article-opinion/.premium/the-israeli-lefts-conceptions-collapsed-too/0000018b-7253-d07a-afcf-76dbc4a00000</link><description></description><pubDate>Sat, 28 Oct 2023 14:34:52 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/opinion/2023-10-28/ty-article-opinion/.premium/the-israeli-lefts-conceptions-collapsed-too/0000018b-7253-d07a-afcf-76dbc4a00000</guid></item><item><title>酒店人满为患，海滩空无一人，阳光明媚的度假城市成为因加沙战争而流离失所的以色列人的中心</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-28/ty-article/.premium/sunny-resort-city-of-eilat-becomes-hub-for-israelis-displaced-by-gaza-war/0000018b-75d9-d2fc-adcf-f7df33e00000</link><description>约 65,000 名加沙边境社区的撤离人员已抵达埃拉特，那里的志愿者正在加紧努力，为空前的涌入者提供住房、食物和援助</description><pubDate>Sat, 28 Oct 2023 11:47:02 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-28/ty-article/.premium/sunny-resort-city-of-eilat-becomes-hub-for-israelis-displaced-by-gaza-war/0000018b-75d9-d2fc-adcf-f7df33e00000</guid></item><item><title>加沙火箭弹击中特拉维夫附近的停车场；内塔尼亚胡会见以色列人质家属</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-28/ty-article-live/gazans-report-heaviest-night-of-attacks-since-outbreak-of-war-as-idf-expands-ground-op/0000018b-7420-d2fc-adcf-f77f6f340000</link><description>以色列国防军主席表示，战争目标需要地面行动，国防部长称战争进入“新阶段” ■ 反坦克导弹袭击以色列军队后，以色列国防军和黎巴嫩军队交火 ■ 内塔尼亚胡会见人质家属代表，在提问后拒绝承担责任自战争爆发以来首次接受媒体报道 ■ 埃尔多安重申哈马斯“不是恐怖组织”后，以色列下令遣返土耳其特使 ■ 阿联酋、沙特阿拉伯谴责以色列在加沙的地面行动 ■ 自 10 月 7 日以来，哈马斯至少造成 1,300 人死亡 ■ 哈马斯卫生部：超过 7,300 名加沙人死亡，约 19,000 人受伤</description><pubDate>Sat, 28 Oct 2023 04:23:37 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-28/ty-article-live/gazans-report-heaviest-night-of-attacks-since-outbreak-of-war-as-idf-expands-ground-op/0000018b-7420-d2fc-adcf-f77f6f340000</guid></item><item><title>加沙火箭弹击中特拉维夫公寓楼，四人受伤，其中一人重伤</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-28/ty-article/.premium/four-people-wounded-one-seriously-after-gaza-rocket-hits-tel-aviv-apartment-building/0000018b-7342-d2fc-adcf-f75ff7030000</link><description></description><pubDate>Fri, 27 Oct 2023 22:39:17 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-28/ty-article/.premium/four-people-wounded-one-seriously-after-gaza-rocket-hits-tel-aviv-apartment-building/0000018b-7342-d2fc-adcf-f75ff7030000</guid></item><item><title>一位集体创伤专家表示，如何治愈整个社会</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-28/ty-article-magazine/.highlight/how-to-heal-an-entire-society-according-to-a-collective-trauma-expert/0000018b-72a6-d51e-a3cb-73eef93b0000</link><description>关掉电视，与孩子们一起出去玩，与朋友见面，回到自己的爱好，玩耍，最重要的是，将生活的精神层面置于中心位置。 《国土报》采访了集体创伤领域的顶尖专家纳撒尼尔·劳尔</description><pubDate>Fri, 27 Oct 2023 21:28:14 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-28/ty-article-magazine/.highlight/how-to-heal-an-entire-society-according-to-a-collective-trauma-expert/0000018b-72a6-d51e-a3cb-73eef93b0000</guid></item><item><title>“等待伟大的灾难”：巴勒斯坦人在约旦河西岸的汽车上发现威胁传单</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-27/ty-article/.premium/wait-for-the-great-nakba-palestinians-find-threatening-leaflets-on-cars-in-west-bank/0000018b-72aa-d1da-a1bb-7fba5a020000</link><description>以色列定居者袭击他们的橄榄园后，来自约旦河西岸城镇代尔伊斯提亚的巴勒斯坦人发现挡风玻璃下夹着传单，警告他们逃往约旦，否则将被强行带走</description><pubDate>Fri, 27 Oct 2023 20:12:45 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-27/ty-article/.premium/wait-for-the-great-nakba-palestinians-find-threatening-leaflets-on-cars-in-west-bank/0000018b-72aa-d1da-a1bb-7fba5a020000</guid></item><item><title>在哈马斯大屠杀中失去亲人的以色列和平活动人士坚守阵地</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-27/ty-article-magazine/.highlight/israeli-peace-activists-who-lost-loved-ones-in-the-hamas-massacre-stand-their-ground/0000018b-7235-d51e-a3cb-737d82d80000</link><description>哈马斯大屠杀的许多受害者及其家人过去和现在都是和平活动人士。幸存的亲属现在不仅要面对深深的悲伤和恐惧，还要面对充满仇恨的评论。但他们个人的悲剧并没有改变他们的鸽派立场。相反</description><pubDate>Fri, 27 Oct 2023 19:35:10 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-27/ty-article-magazine/.highlight/israeli-peace-activists-who-lost-loved-ones-in-the-hamas-massacre-stand-their-ground/0000018b-7235-d51e-a3cb-737d82d80000</guid></item><item><title>哈马斯正在加沙的地堡中重新调整中东的力量平衡</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/middle-east-news/2023-10-27/ty-article/.premium/from-its-bunkers-in-gaza-hamas-is-rejiggering-the-balance-of-power-in-the-middle-east/0000018b-71a6-dec3-a59f-f5f7c1a30000</link><description>哈马斯的袭击迫使卡塔尔、沙特阿拉伯、埃及、土耳其和阿拉伯联合酋长国组成了一个不稳定的联盟。目前尚不清楚他们中的任何人是否能够拆除目前在加沙的炸弹</description><pubDate>Fri, 27 Oct 2023 19:18:21 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/middle-east-news/2023-10-27/ty-article/.premium/from-its-bunkers-in-gaza-hamas-is-rejiggering-the-balance-of-power-in-the-middle-east/0000018b-71a6-dec3-a59f-f5f7c1a30000</guid></item><item><title>拜登纪念生命之树枪击事件五周年，援引以色列哈马斯大屠杀</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/us-news/2023-10-27/ty-article/.premium/biden-marks-fifth-anniversary-of-tree-of-life-shooting-invokes-hamas-massacre-in-israel/0000018b-71eb-dec3-a59f-f5fb90f60000</link><description>拜登在纪念匹兹堡被白人民族主义者杀害的 11 名犹太人时表示，“纪念活动是在大屠杀以来对犹太人来说最致命的一天之后进行的”</description><pubDate>Fri, 27 Oct 2023 18:45:26 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/us-news/2023-10-27/ty-article/.premium/biden-marks-fifth-anniversary-of-tree-of-life-shooting-invokes-hamas-massacre-in-israel/0000018b-71eb-dec3-a59f-f5fb90f60000</guid></item></channel></rss>